reviewText: It is great to relive childhood memories and to have Punky Brewster back in our home I grew up on these so it was a wonderful present for my husband great job wood recorder please keep me posted when you get more awesome job
In great condition enjoyed watching them

My favorite show as a child & it's been a joy watching this again & even sharing it w/my cousins that I watched this show w/as a young child! Thank you for the wonderful childhood memories re-lived!! :D
Daughter loved the gift of this DVD set which brought back fond memories of her childhood. She'll pass this down when she has children of her own.

The family is a big fan of Punky Brewster so I couldn't go wrong. Shipped on time. Only issue is the cases are different? I figured that buying the set, it would look like a set...but two are in alike cases while the other to aren't.
Bought so long along I don't remember.  They were a gift and I don't recall any complaints.  Must have been okay.
The DVD set brings back a lot of childhood memories and is an entertainer that the whole family can enjoy.
I grew up watching this show and my children enjoy it as much as I did. Thanks and the movies are excellent.

I WATCHED THIS SERIES WHEN IT WAS FIRST ON TV,AND THEY WERE GOOD.THE GOOD THING ABOUT THE STORIES WAS THEY WERE ALL KINDS FROM COMEDY TO SAD,FROM ADVENTURE TO ACTION..AND I THOUGHT SOILIL MOON FRYE WAS A GOOD ACTRESSES,CAUSE SHE CARRIED SOME OF THE STORIES ON HER OWN..A WHAT YOU CALL A SPECIAL SERIES
I watched Punky Brewter as a kid and now that I have a little girl, I wanted her to grow up watching "Punky Power"!!!
